Yes, we could delete this, and declare the buildNative as a DefaultTask, something like this in QuarkusPlugin:
Task buildNative = tasks.create(BUILD_NATIVE_TASK_NAME, DefaultTask.class);

But this will be a breaking change instead of a deprecation. Is that ok? or should we first release the @Deprecated and then this update?

